dc_title_s: Ontario soybean grain prices, 2000 to May 2010 [Canada]
dc_description_s:
This dataset contains Ontario soybean grain prices collected by University of Guelph, Ridgetown Campus. The dataset includes daily prices of agricultural commodities at individual elevators in Ontario. Daily highs and lows are given for each commodity, as well as, daily Bank of Canada exchange rates.

This dataset includes data for January 2000 to May 2010, and September 2010.
